He caught me completely of guard.

6
00:00:11,383 --> 00:00:13,259
We dated almost twenty years ago.

7
00:00:13,310 --> 00:00:14,406
He was crazy.

8
00:00:14,536 --> 00:00:17,070
Veronica, are you in immediate life threatening danger?

9
00:00:17,121 --> 00:00:18,960
