10
00:00:19,011 --> 00:00:21,464
If she needs me, I'm gonna come through, just like she would for me.

11
00:00:21,515 --> 00:00:26,007
Where I'm from, the girl who you make out with is the one you do favors for.

12
00:00:26,701 --> 00:00:27,755
Who are you?

13
