14
00:00:44,022 --> 00:00:46,636
I was just gonna come outside to grab you.

15
00:00:47,918 --> 00:00:49,285
Food is ready.

16
00:00:50,162 --> 00:00:51,652
I'm not hungry, mom.

17
00:00:52,263 --> 00:00:54,743
I just met somebody out in the driveway.

18
00:00:55,212 --> 00:00:56,720
Wallace, what's wrong?

19
00:00:56,771 --> 00:00:59,182
A guy from Chicago --
he said he knew you.

20
00:00:59,233 --> 00:01:01,193
Name Nathan woods ring a bell?

21
00:01:01,732 --> 00:01:02,763
Oh, Wallace.

22
00:01:02,883 --> 00:01:03,935
Is it true?

23
00:01:04,677 --> 00:01:06,773
- Baby --
- No, just tell me if it's true.

24
00:01:06,824 --> 00:01:09,089
You were never supposed to see that man.

25
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:10,081
Is he still here?

26
00:01:10,132 --> 00:01:11,005
"That man"?

27
00:01:11,056 --> 00:01:14,086
You got to be kidding.
Why don't you just call him what he really is?

28
00:01:14,137 --> 00:01:17,229
So, who did we put in the ground back in cleveland?

29
00:01:17,914 --> 00:01:20,021
Who was it I cried for all those months?

30
00:01:20,072 --> 00:01:21,278
