124
00:06:56,502 --> 00:06:59,056
I got nothing but good sides, baby.

125
00:07:04,982 --> 00:07:09,377
Your grandma wants me to remind you that you're a risk-taker, with an...

126
00:07:10,122 --> 00:07:13,206
