132
00:07:24,425 --> 00:07:25,475
I'm sorry, child.

133
00:07:25,526 --> 00:07:27,268
This card's been declined.

134
00:07:39,420 --> 00:07:40,324
Lip balm?

135
00:07:40,731 --> 00:07:43,387
It's a surge of lip-quenching fruit flavor.

136
00:07:44,677 --> 00:07:48,457
Wallace said I would find you here.
I need to ask you something.

137
00:07:52,484 --> 00:07:53,974
I'm in some trouble.

138
00:07:54,182 --> 00:07:55,771
I didn't know who else to go to.

139
00:07:55,822 --> 00:07:58,084
Wallace said that you might help me.

140
