<i>bring it on, bring it on, yeah</i>

145
00:08:18,138 --> 00:08:21,265
<i>just remember me when</i>

146
00:08:21,613 --> 00:08:23,594
<i>we used to be friends</i>

147
00:08:23,869 --> 00:08:25,508
<i>a long time ago</i>

148
