<i>we used to be friends</i>

149
00:08:29,525 --> 00:08:33,433
<i>Saison 2 - Episode 5
"Blast from the past"</i>

150
00:08:35,244 --> 00:08:37,738
someone stole my credit card and maxed it out.

151
00:08:37,789 --> 00:08:40,120
So call the credit card company.
They'll erase the charges.

152
00:08:40,171 --> 00:08:43,147
I've done that. It's not the bill I'm worried about.

153
00:08:43,198 --> 00:08:44,982
What are you worried about?

154
00:08:45,198 --> 00:08:48,864
My friend cora borrows my stuff all the time.

155
00:08:48,915 --> 00:08:50,958
It's like she doesn't have clothes of her own.

156
00:08:51,009 --> 00:08:53,350
And, well...

157
00:08:53,432 --> 00:08:55,876
I noticed my card was missing after I went shopping with her.

158
00:08:55,927 --> 00:08:59,856
Then I found it in my car, like someone had deliberately put it back.

159
00:08:59,907 --> 00:09:01,785
I don't want to just accuse her.

160
00:09:01,836 --> 00:09:03,485
So you want me to prove she did it?

161
00:09:03,536 --> 00:09:06,116
No. I want you to prove that she didn'T.

162
00:09:06,186 --> 00:09:08,674
She's the only friend that I have here.

163
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,618
I...

164
00:09:10,315 --> 00:09:12,275
