Hank Ditten...

224
00:13:02,982 --> 00:13:04,880
And Wallace Fennel.

225
00:13:04,931 --> 00:13:06,557
Yeah! Go, Wallace!

226
00:13:09,090 --> 00:13:10,270
All right, man!

